{"type": "article", "id": 15938, "title": "线条灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-12T07:11:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110631NGb8qh0pSjPCQMDx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t热爱玩弄线条的英国设计师 Michael Anastassiades 带来了他的新作，用黄铜杆和条状 LED 灯组成不同造型。灯有 0.5 米和 1 米两种长度，与黄铜杆的直径相同，它们时而并排时而错位，在对称与不对称当中组成有趣的平衡。细微的变化中蕴含了很大的不同，而简单的造型和孤单的投影都诠释极简的审美。<a href=\"http://studiomichaelanastassiades.com/news\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里是他的主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143403TXQ2DLRxzIlemZOK.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1112\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.18803419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261434038shmUjwXJWNAT2pt.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"623\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143404ZK8AlW937JyDIOMj.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"739\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}